            <div style="font-size: 36px; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 8px;">&#128736;</div>
            <div style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #1F2937; margin-bottom: 4px;">Dual Road Frontage</div>
            <div style="font-size: 13px; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.5;">Excellent accessibility from two major roadways.</div>
          </div>
        </mj-text>
